summary: New tattoo set for UNP body.
descriptionHtml:
Previous versions here:
http://www.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28651
http://www.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28836


=============

This version includes couple new tattoos, see attached images for more details.


As requested, I included the psd file with the archive, along with the 5 basic preset dds files for those who prefer not to have to deal with photoshop.


=============


Installation: (These WILL override my V1/2 designs)

Download, extract, select ONE of the options, backup original, and replace original.




Uninstallation:

Remove femalebody_1.dds, restore original.
author: Elewin
